---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import MapView from "../components/MapView.astro";
---
<Base title="Leaves.PH · the map" pathname="/map">
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 pt-10 pb-6">
    <p class="kicker mb-3">FEATURE &middot; INTERACTIVE</p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-editorial gap-x-12 gap-y-4 items-end">
      <h1 class="font-display font-medium tracking-tight text-ink-900 leading-[0.95]" style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);">
        Every canopy patch above 5 m, mapped per LGU, year by year.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-700 leading-[1.7] max-w-prose">
        Slide the year. The choropleth retunes. The Meta canopy 1 m raster sits underneath. Click any LGU to open its dossier: 8-year curve, Hansen cumulative loss, ESA 2021 cross-check. Crown polygons (242,810 individual canopy patches) load at street zoom when the .pmtiles file ships.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <MapView />
</Base>
